---
title: Sausages in Sage Onion Gravy with creamy butternut mash
description: Forget about bangers and mash. These sizzling pan-fried pork sausages and creamy butternut squash are the ultimate rich and warming dish—made all the better by being soused in sage onion gravy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R04_W05_IE_IECFP0168-2_KB_Main_high-828a1b9d.jpg
